%description
The Citizens' Service Bureau of the City of St. Louis is a clearing house
for non-emergency service requests. This package provides functions for
downloading, categorizing problem requests, cleaning and subsetting CSB
data, and projecting the data using the x and y coordinates included with
CSB data releases.

